Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I return to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Makise Kurisu dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cracking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:52.89,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Paradox Meltdown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is today the last day of Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of cute cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not really interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Okarin's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said we weren't doing the cracking, \Nand that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's gonna reach a high of 35!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hydration is the best way to prevent heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to Comima today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really sunny out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}August 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each D-mail I undid delayed \NMayuri's death by one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Erasing Suzuha's mail made the events \Nof the 13th occur on the 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feyris, Rukako, Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each one pushed it back a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then in this world line, Mayuri dies on the 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, before 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost sold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one for Daru-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and there was a book on a \Nrobot anime I thought you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if there's anywhere you'd like to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to think about, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Organization assassins hiding in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something to escape their clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not careful, they might find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the original plan until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think any bad people like that are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet back here at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're selling juice over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before that time, find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way for her to survive without \Nchanging world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.02,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to help Hashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A notepad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A list of circles at Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at the second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously having you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we haven't touched it for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain what's going on, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri will die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're doing the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To erase the first D-mail you sent—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to think of a way to \Nsave Mayuri without the cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have changed. This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I won't be able \Nto think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to stop by the lab, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii was thinking of getting some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Almost time for her to die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. That never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You barely went to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted to check something out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've shown you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many things Mayushii \Nknows more than Okarin about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never gone to Comima together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Mayushii was happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see Rukako looking \Nembarrassed in his cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if he had, he would've been really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Ruka-kun would have gotten \Nhis photo on all the blogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he'd have become a worldwide superstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Mayushii would have seen it \Nand said, "He's come a long way."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be even better if Okarin cosplayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, you'd also have to cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... We'll call Rukako and Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can convince them to cosplay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, then I,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma, mad scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shall make my cosplay debut at Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kurisu-chan was interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Mayushii will try her best to \Ndo it by the next Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My watch isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't go through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll stop it from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I let that car hit me... If I die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}something has to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally, I was useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii was useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see the stars from here, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.60,Sign21A,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you. \NKurisu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been up here, on the roof, for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without a sound. I got worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm not worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You yourself said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought the FBI would come, \Nand you got scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to be thought of as a law-abiding citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your normal, hotshot attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I act like that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mad scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew within five seconds of meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you time leap again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've helped you with everything so far, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made it this far by \Nthinking things through together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha and Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrificed the things they loved the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, this is how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, you were crying back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida was concerned, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thought maybe you had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,July 28th...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri and I went to \NDr. Nakabachi's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, I saw Makise Kurise collapsed\Nafter being stabbed by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent a text to Daru's cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was connected to the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The message that moved us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the beta world line to the alpha world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deleting that message from SERN's database,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returning to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means going back to that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we return to the beta world line...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we undo that first D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daru-kun told me you were acting odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii's been so busy with Comima,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she couldn't spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you used to talk to Mayushii about \Nall kinds of stuff, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were four Organization generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geppu, Sudachi, Seiyuu, and Jakkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genbu, Suzaku, Seiryuu, Byakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really liked hearing about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mayushii is ever a burden, tell me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mayushii can do anything for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From your voice, I can guess what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go see her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to come up with any answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you do stay here, talking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were sitting here alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should go see Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that will happen if you \Nstay and worry is that you'll hurt my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii. I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the cosplayers said Mayushii left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see me because it's Obon. \NRight, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only been having scary dreams lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dreams, terrible things happen to Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets shot with a pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or she's in a car accident or run over by a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything seems like it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary, and it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to scream for help, as loud as I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the end of the dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin always comes to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii says, "Thank you, Okarin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't hear her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He holds Mayushii, and he looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he never cries, \Nbut you can tell he really wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii says, "I'm sorry." \NBut he doesn't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk about something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, there are lots of new lab members!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Moeka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ruka-kun, and Feyris-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan is super-smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she talks about all these \Nreally hard things with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin looks happy that he gets to talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, sometimes I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time Mayushii went to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the beginning of spring, but it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to the lab after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was cleaning up the room, he came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I said, "Welcome back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't say, "I'm back."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Good work."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, every day after that, I'd go there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for about two hours, and we'd barely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't bad. We were simply there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passed so slowly, and it was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii thought she really was like a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing good happened, but it was good anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand... You saw some kind of illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may be an attack by \NOrganization General Illusion Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I bet that Illusion Contactor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think he's a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I haven't spent much time \Ntalking with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be that when I saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he's really suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he's always about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know he's thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a burden to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I was talking about \Nsomething sad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Mayushii's been lonely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, I can't stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always know where my hostage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't ever escape from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hououin Kyouma,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am not so weak that I need you \Nto worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes that I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get another Upa gatchapon, right?
